Interface Set<E>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Collection<E>
    All Known Implementing Classes:

    public interface Set<E>
extends Collection<E>
    Set interface represents the Set which extends from Collection interface in Java. Set is extended from Collection interface. This interface is a generic interface.
